dataStructure.name: sid.org.tmforum.tip.enterprise.risk.sec.evt.AuditRecordSecurityEvent
dataStructure.description:
The elements that are used to extend the base event type for audit records consist of a single text field to contain log data. The Common Event Expression (CEE) standard to build out the common elements that can be captured and returned as part of an audit record event.

This entity is optional
dataStructure.label: AuditRecordSecurityEvent

child.name: logData
child.description:
Text from logs that captured information relevant to the event.

This element is generated from an attribute.

This attribute is mandatory

This attribute is AVC enabled
child.label: logData
